PART IV — USER RESPONSIBILITY AND ACCEPTABLE USE
================================================================================

By installing, using, or distributing MilitechOS, you agree that:

  1. LEGAL COMPLIANCE
     You are solely and entirely responsible for ensuring your use of
     MilitechOS and all included software complies with all applicable local,
     national, and international laws and regulations in your jurisdiction.

  2. SECURITY AND RESEARCH TOOLS
     MilitechOS includes network analysis, security research, and penetration
     testing tools (including but not limited to Wireshark, Nmap, Aircrack-ng,
     and related utilities). These tools are provided exclusively for:
       · Legal security research
       · Authorized penetration testing
       · Educational and academic purposes
       · Testing systems you own or have explicit written permission to test

     USE OF THESE TOOLS AGAINST SYSTEMS YOU DO NOT OWN OR DO NOT HAVE
     EXPLICIT AUTHORIZATION TO TEST IS ILLEGAL IN MOST JURISDICTIONS AND
     IS STRICTLY PROHIBITED. Militech-Dev accepts zero responsibility for
     any illegal use of security tools included in MilitechOS.

  3. RADIO AND COMMUNICATIONS TOOLS
     MilitechOS includes radio communication software (including but not
     limited to Direwolf, WSJTX, JS8Call, GQRX, and related utilities).
     You are solely responsible for:
       · Obtaining all required licenses and permits for radio transmission
         in your jurisdiction (e.g. amateur radio license, FCC license)
       · Complying with all applicable radio frequency regulations
       · Ensuring your radio use does not interfere with licensed services

     Militech-Dev accepts no responsibility for unlicensed or illegal
     radio transmissions made using tools included in MilitechOS.

  4. PRIVACY AND ANONYMITY TOOLS
     MilitechOS includes privacy tools (including but not limited to
     Tor Browser, VeraCrypt, and related utilities). These tools are
     provided for legitimate privacy protection. You are solely responsible
     for ensuring your use of these tools complies with applicable law.

  5. GPS AND LOCATION TOOLS
     GPS and mapping tools included in MilitechOS are provided for
     navigation and research purposes only. Any use for stalking,
     surveillance, or harassment is strictly prohibited and illegal.

  6. DATA AND SYSTEM RESPONSIBILITY
     You are solely responsible for backing up your data before installing
     or using MilitechOS. Militech-Dev accepts no responsibility for any
     data loss, system damage, or hardware failure resulting from the
     installation or use of MilitechOS.

  7. SURVIVAL AND INFORMATIONAL CONTENT
     Any survival, medical, navigational, or informational content included
     in or accessible through MilitechOS is provided for educational purposes
     only. It does not constitute professional advice. Always consult qualified
     professionals for medical, legal, safety, or survival decisions.
     Militech-Dev accepts no responsibility for decisions made based on
     information accessed through MilitechOS.

