PART V — EXPORT CONTROL
================================================================================

MilitechOS includes cryptographic and security software that may be subject
to export control laws and regulations. This is because encryption software
is legally restricted from being distributed to certain countries and
individuals under US law (applicable due to GitHub's US jurisdiction) and
other international regulations.

By downloading, installing, or using MilitechOS, you confirm that:

  · You are not located in a country currently subject to international
    embargo or comprehensive trade restrictions
  · You are not listed on any government denied-parties, sanctions, or
    restricted entities list
  · You will comply with all applicable export control laws and regulations
    in your country and internationally

If you are unsure whether these restrictions apply to you, do not download
or use MilitechOS.

